Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸腐于野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊断于利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心爱之人 且赴黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨我可就找错门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨的话就恨德川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨骏府的家康大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨将军继承人之争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 诅咒自己为何生在甲贺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.36,0:03:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天 终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.65,0:04:26.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦…之…介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说听见打斗的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.27,0:06:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在那儿抖什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是胧出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.32,0:06:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么交待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿起剑吧 胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不得不置我于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我的双目被封
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的双眼也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺人干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我自己封住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想目睹与卍谷人的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这双眼睛重见光明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺只剩我一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺也只剩下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拔剑啊 胧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不杀胧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要背叛甲贺 背叛卍谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.05,0:08:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人欺骗您 陷害您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是锷隐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.46,0:09:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之…介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的…安居之所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在于…此世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一个人活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒性…消失…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想…我不想杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让任何人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:12.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甲贺人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺弦之介来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天膳大人又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.62,0:13:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫要惊慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳是不死的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是都知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人 扶他起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那颗脑袋给他放回原处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:14:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是关系到竹千代少爷 也关系到我阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也关系到你们命运的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 胧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心药师寺天膳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许还没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会不死的秘术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也非忍术范畴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身体里寄宿着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道那究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那传说早在我出生之前就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有确认之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 依我之见 寄生在他体内的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 说太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对今后路还长的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我也老糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛能看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不太对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.68,0:17:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就藏在…胧身后…的台阶下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对今后路还长的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等甲贺卍谷一族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺锷隐一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身怀可怕忍法秘术的双方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以长年宿怨为由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:28.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实为愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对今后路还长的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.53,0:20:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…胧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才天膳所说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我的身后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.03,0:20:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺着身受重伤又了中毒的甲贺人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死无反抗之力的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有损伊贺之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说什么话 一点不像忍者的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火速派人报告服部半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.16,0:21:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快备马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在双方忍众仲裁的半藏大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.99,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可有异议？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…异议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂静暮春
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然楚楚稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.94,0:23:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垢的两个灵魂坠入蓝色冥暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同转瞬即逝的泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.08,0:23:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消逝在青蓝月辉的他界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏于心的羁绊 飘摇的悲恋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数度轮回之后再续前缘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.61,0:23:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越千万暗夜再结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.85,0:24:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,basilisk 甲贺忍法帖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终话

